OL,3,CSpeeding drug-driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling grandma on mobility scooter
OL,6,FA speeding driver who hit and killed a
OL,7,Fgrandmother on a mobility scooter in
OL,8,FNottingham has been jailed for 4 years.
OL,10,F31-year-old Rayner Middleton admitted
OL,11,Fcausing the death of Doreen 'Mar'
OL,12,FRaynor in a crash on 4 March, 2023
OL,13,Fwhile she was more than double the
OL,14,Flegal limit of benzoylecgonine - a
OL,15,Fmetabolite of cocaine.
OL,17,FNottingham Crown Court heard Middleton
OL,18,Fhad consumed drink and drugs the night
OL,19,Fbefore she went to pick up her son,
OL,20,Fwhen she drove her Audio A1 at nearly
OL,21,F50mph in a 30mph zone.
