OL,6,FShe tested below the legal limit for
OL,7,Falcohol when she was breathalysed, but
OL,8,Fhad some alcohol in her system.
OL,10,FMrs Raynor was thrown out of her
OL,11,Fmobility scooter in the crash while
OL,12,Fout getting vegetables to make a
OL,13,Ffamily dinner.
OL,15,FShe died later that day at Queen's
OL,16,FMedical Centre.
