OL,3,CSpeeding drug-driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling grandma on mobility scooter
OL,6,FProsecution barrister Nicholas Bleaney
OL,7,Ftold the court, filled with members of
OL,8,Fboth the defendant's and victim's
OL,9,Ffamilies: "Mrs Raynor was a month shy
OL,10,Fof her 90th birthday in March of 2023.
OL,12,F"She had some mobility issues due to
OL,13,Fan old injury. She used an electric
OL,14,Fmobility scooter on most days, this
OL,15,Fbeing a device to ensure she retains
OL,16,Fas much of her independence as
OL,17,Fpossible."
