OL,3,CSpeeding drug-driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling grandma on mobility scooter
OL,6,FThe court heard that the traffic
OL,7,Flights turned amber as Middleton was
OL,8,Fdriving through the crossing, while
OL,9,Fthe pedestrian light for Mrs Raynor
OL,10,Fwas red when she entered the road on
OL,11,Fher scooter.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor continued: "There was a
OL,14,Fcollision which caused Mrs Raynor to
OL,15,Fbe thrown out of her mobility scooter
OL,16,Fand suffer very serious injuries."
