OL,6,FMrs Raynor's daughter, Melanie
OL,7,FFrearson read a statement to the court
OL,8,Fthat said: "She was known to everyone
OL,9,Fas 'Mar'. She had 13 children ` one of
OL,10,Fthem was an abandoned baby who was
OL,11,Fleft in her care.
OL,13,F"This shows the type of person she was
OL,14,F` completely mother to all. I feel so
OL,15,Fangry that I have been cheated of
OL,16,Fhaving Mar to hold me when I'm not
OL,17,Fwell. She got me through so much.
OL,19,F"Mar should have died peacefully of
OL,20,Fold age, not in the way she died."
