OL,3,CSpeeding drug-driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling grandma on mobility scooter
OL,6,F"She has expressed genuine remorse for
OL,7,Fthe loss of life."
OL,9,FSentencing Middleton, Judge Steven
OL,10,FCoupland said the defendant "chose to
OL,11,Fdrive in an aggressive way" at a speed
OL,12,Fthat was inappropriate for the road.
OL,14,FHe added that the combination of each
OL,15,Fsubstance was "likely to have
OL,16,Fincreased the effects of the other"
OL,17,Fwhen Middleton was driving.
