OL,6,FHe said: "Her family and friends will
OL,7,Fsuffer her loss for the rest of their
OL,8,Flives. Their future will be marked by
OL,9,Fan empty seat at the table and a gap
OL,10,Fin photographs."
OL,12,FThe judge also disqualified Middleton
OL,13,Ffrom driving for four years.
